      <title>马士基认为红海危机将对世界贸易产生更深远影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/maersk-sees-deeper-impact-to-world-trade-from-red-sea-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球贸易的风向标马士基集团 (A.P. Moller-Maersk A/S) 表示，红海拥堵带来的连锁反应对全球供应链的影响比之前预期的要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/maersk-sees-deeper-impact-to-world-trade-from-red-sea-disruption</guid>
